man Vishal is fucking awesome, i don't listen to Bollywood music much but when i saw him on sa re ga ma as a judge,  my first impression of him where, is this some kind of jumped of person pretending to be a music producer ?

admittedly he has his own rebellious style, but this performance here is +10 :D

music producers should stop catering to Bollywood garbage item songs and other bullshit and go make ral music again like there and create their own platform and stop being dependent on Bollywood film release schedules.

Bollywood producers/Movie producers should stand in line to work with these people, not the other way around. music producers should push these kind of music to the general audiences and not the typical formula of love song/item song/hit song shit.
